workflow Audit Coil port bugs
runner deepseek

agent audit
title Analyze main.coil for port-bug patterns
prompt Given docs/coil-port-bugs.md and src/main.coil, identify any code that could trigger the same bugs (missing Eq bounds, field-on-call, etc.). Include file:line and bug pattern.
after none

agent prioritize
title Prioritize fix candidates
prompt Using the audit output, rank findings by severity and draft text descriptions of the top 2 fixes, referencing the bug doc.
after audit
